<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.10">
<l>pāñcacaṉ ṉiyattaip paṟpanā paṉōṭum</l>
<l>vāynta peruñcuṟṟa mākkiya voṇputuvai</l>
<l>ēyntapukaḻp paṭṭarpirāṉ kōtaitami ḻīraintum</l>
<l>āyntētta vallā ravaru maṇukkarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those capable of praising [Him], reflecting on all ten Tamil [verses by]</l>
<l>Kōtai, [daughter of] the chief priest of a befitting fame from the pretty Putuvai,</l>
<l>who created a great, suitable relationship for Pāñcajanya with Padmanābha</l>
<l>will be close [to Him] indeed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
